      "type": "incident_body",
      "details": "5xx error rate on `/v2/checkout` exceeded threshold (>5%) for 10 minutes.\n\n## Metrics\n\n- **Current 5xx rate**: 8.3% (baseline: 0.2%)\n- **Affected regions**: us-east-1, eu-west-1\n- **Started**: ~2 hours ago (correlates with v2.8 deploy)\n\n## Runbook\n\n1. Check error traces: [Datadog APM](https://app.datadoghq.com/apm/traces?query=service:api-gateway%20status:error)\n2. Check recent deploys:\n```bash\nkubectl rollout history deployment/api-gateway -n prod\n```\n3. If deploy-related, rollback:\n```bash\nkubectl rollout undo deployment/api-gateway -n prod\nkubectl rollout status deployment/api-gateway -n prod\n```\n4. Verify recovery in [error rate dashboard](https://grafana.internal/d/api-errors)\n\n> **Note**: Do NOT restart pods without checking connection pools first.\n> See [runbook](https://wiki.internal/runbooks/api-gateway-errors) for details.\n\n## Recent changes\n\n- v2.8 deployed 2h ago by @john.doe via [PR #1847](https://github.com/acme/api-gateway/pull/1847)\n- Added new payment validation middleware"
