      "type": "incident_body",
      "details": "SSL certificate for `*.api.acme.com` expires in **7 days**.\n\n## Certificate details\n\n```\nSubject:    *.api.acme.com\nIssuer:     Let's Encrypt Authority X3\nNot After:  2026-03-25 12:00:00 UTC\nSerial:     03:a1:b2:c3:d4:e5:f6\n```\n\n## Runbook\n\n1. Check cert-manager status:\n```bash\nkubectl get certificates -n prod\nkubectl describe certificate api-wildcard -n prod\n```\n2. If auto-renewal failed, check DNS challenge:\n```bash\nkubectl logs -n cert-manager deploy/cert-manager -f | grep api.acme.com\n```\n3. Manual renewal (last resort):\n```bash\nkubectl delete certificate api-wildcard -n prod\nkubectl apply -f manifests/certificates/api-wildcard.yaml\n```\n\n## References\n\n- [Cert management wiki](https://wiki.internal/certs)\n- [cert-manager docs](https://cert-manager.io/docs/troubleshooting/)"
